    },
    {
      "start": 92.7,
      "end": 93.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.0,
      "end": 94.24,
      "text": "What kind of food?"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.74,
      "end": 96.68,
      "text": "좀 더, 그 퓨전이라고 했으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 96.68,
      "end": 98.28,
      "text": "아주 화려하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.28,
      "end": 100.72,
      "text": "뭔가 음식에 좀 더 포커스를 두고"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.72,
      "end": 102.18,
      "text": "클로즈업 할 수 있는"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.18,
      "end": 103.82,
      "text": "그런 장면이 많이 있지 않았을까"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.82,
      "end": 105.6,
      "text": "예상을 하면서 봤단 말이에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 106.06,
      "end": 108.12,
      "text": "You're going to have to watch a cooking documentary."
    },
    {
      "start": 108.64,
      "end": 109.94,
      "text": "Cooking documentary 보세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 110.34,
      "end": 111.38,
      "text": "Good recommendation."
    },
    {
      "start": 111.38,
      "end": 114.22,
      "text": "그리고 또 타이틀이요."
    },
    {
      "start": 114.42,
      "end": 115.76,
      "text": "It's also about cooking, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 115.88,
      "end": 117.38,
      "text": "Cookie diary이잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 118.12,
      "end": 120.82,
      "text": "근데 생각보다 요리가 많이 나오지는 않았단 말이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 121.36,
      "end": 126.5,
      "text": "So, I didn't have an appetite while watching this movie at night."
    },
    {
      "start": 126.76,
      "end": 128.22,
      "text": "It didn't make you hungry?"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.84,
      "end": 129.36,
      "text": "Thankfully."
    },
    {
      "start": 129.6,
      "end": 130.24,
      "text": "Oh, that's a good thing."
    },
    {
      "start": 130.24,
      "end": 130.8,
      "text": "At night, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 130.8,
      "end": 132.36,
      "text": "Because you say you're on a diet."
    },
    {
      "start": 132.44,
      "end": 132.72,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 132.92,
      "end": 136.38,
      "text": "You're trying to avoid late night snacks, late night meals."
    },
    {
      "start": 136.88,
      "end": 138.0,
      "text": "This movie was good for you."
    },
    {
      "start": 138.08,
      "end": 138.26,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 138.62,
      "end": 140.54,
      "text": "식욕이 전혀 자극이 안 됐더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 141.62,
      "end": 142.8,
      "text": "Oh, 전혀 효과 있었네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 142.88,
      "end": 143.12,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.32,
      "end": 144.72,
      "text": "Anyway, do you like fusion food?"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.72,
      "end": 148.9,
      "text": "I like any kind of food, as long as it's good food."
    },
    {
      "start": 149.14,
      "end": 156.12,
      "text": "But for fusion, oftentimes, it takes a lot of time and effort to make quality fusion."
    },
    {
      "start": 156.22,
      "end": 156.64,
      "text": "I agree."
    },
    {
      "start": 156.92,
      "end": 159.3,
      "text": "So, it's sold at very, very high prices."
    },
    {
      "start": 159.5,
      "end": 159.74,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 159.74,
      "end": 162.36,
      "text": "Like the good fusion food is very expensive."
    },
    {
      "start": 162.52,
      "end": 162.92,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 163.26,
      "end": 166.94,
      "text": "So, I usually prefer just good basic cuisine."
    },
    {
      "start": 167.16,
      "end": 171.08,
      "text": "Korean, American, Italian, just basic cuisine."
    },
    {
      "start": 171.08,
      "end": 171.72,
      "text": "그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 172.08,
      "end": 176.66,
      "text": "웬만한 음식을 가리지 않고 다 잘 드신다라는 크리스 씨의 이야기를 들으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 176.66,
      "end": 179.4,
      "text": "역시 사랑받는 크서방."
    },
    {
      "start": 180.36,
      "end": 182.84,
      "text": "사람이 잘 먹으면 복이 와요."
    },
    {
      "start": 183.36,
      "end": 185.12,
      "text": "이런 명언까지 감사합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 185.12,
      "end": 188.04,
      "text": "이게 확실히 fusion 요리는요."
    },
    {
      "start": 188.12,
      "end": 191.02,
      "text": "말씀하신 것처럼 더 연구가 많이 필요 되잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 191.78,
      "end": 197.82,
      "text": "익숙한 맛이면서도 또 거기에 약간 독특함이 들어있어야지 그게 매력적인 요리가 되는 거니까."
    },
    {
      "start": 197.82,
      "end": 198.3,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 198.44,
      "end": 206.9,
      "text": "So, for cheap fusion food, sometimes restaurants sell cheap fusion food, but oftentimes, 이것도, 저것도 아닌 그런 거 많아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 206.96,
      "end": 207.32,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 207.68,
      "end": 211.94,
      "text": "So, I just prefer basic, 뭐, 가장백반 or basic spaghetti."
    },
    {
      "start": 212.14,
      "end": 212.76,
      "text": "배고프다."
    },
    {
      "start": 212.88,
      "end": 213.98,
      "text": "Steak and potatoes."
    },
    {
      "start": 214.44,
      "end": 215.12,
      "text": "배고프다."
    },
    {
      "start": 215.2,
      "end": 215.58,
      "text": "어떡하지?"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.74,
      "end": 216.26,
      "text": "그만할게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 216.76,
      "end": 216.94,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.28,
      "end": 218.72,
      "text": "일단 오늘 내용 듣고 올게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 219.66,
      "end": 221.08,
      "text": "We're not packing this away, are we?"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.7,
      "end": 223.9,
      "text": "Those recipes are pretty great, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.26,
      "end": 224.6,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 224.86,
      "end": 225.5,
      "text": "I love them."
    },
    {
      "start": 225.5,
      "end": 227.26,
      "text": "She was such a good cook."
    },
    {
      "start": 228.04,
      "end": 230.44,
      "text": "I guess it skipped a generation when it's straight to you."
    },
    {
      "start": 231.08,
