      "text": "I can have these."
    },
    {
      "start": 234.12,
      "end": 235.62,
      "text": "I think she'd want you to have them."
    },
    {
      "start": 236.72,
      "end": 239.46,
      "text": "Oh, his grandmother must have been a good cook, too."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.74,
      "end": 240.22,
